Text.string: Man, that was AWESOME! You kicked Maliwan's ass! Or whatever.
You really held your own on Athenas. Not sayin' I'm impressed, but I'm not NOT sayin' that, you know?
If anything goes missing, it's not me. Hermes is a total klepto, just saying. Oh! Or blame it on Claptrap. Yeah. Claptrap.
Maliwan is the worst!||—Except for Hyperion, Dahl, and even Atlas back in the day, I guess. Maya says corporations are like bandits, but legal. That's enough to keep you up at night!
So glad I'm not on Athenas. The smelly monks, the gross ratches, the stupid bells...||[sigh] I guess it wasn't so bad.
Glad we got that Key fragment off Athenas before Maliwan snatched it.
I know we're only here because Maliwan totally trashed my home. But that said, it's sorta nice to be off Athenas for a change.
Way to show Katagawa what's what, Vault Hunter. Or whatever.
Vault Hunters: two, Maliwan: zero! Just sayin'.
Looks like you saved Atlas. Nice work. I dunno about that Rhys guy. Seems sorta hyper-sketch, y'know?
Lilith's gone. Maya's gone. It's just us, now. So we gotta pick up the slack, yeah?
Hey Vault Hunter. Think Lilith is still... no, nevermind. Dumb thought.
We did it, we saved the universe! Wish Maya was around to see this.

Hey, you checked out Lilith's room yet? Look, I'm all for respecting the dead, but we don't know that she's dead. It's not pillaging if they're still alive. And maybe there's somethin' important in there, ya know?
Pretty sweet setup we got here. Lots of stuff to steal—I mean, admire. From afar.
Yeah, hey. You're bored too, huh?
Didn't take long for Marcus to ban me from his shop. Jokes on him, I took his padlock. Now I can't go in and he can't leave.
I... I can't believe she's gone.
I don't know why I ever wanted to be a Vault Hunter in the first place. Maya never talked about the bad parts... or maybe I just never listened.
Just... leave me alone for a little while, okay?
Look. I don't want to talk right now. Have fun savin' the galaxy.
[sigh] Maya... she's gone.
Oh, hey. So, Claptrap said you launched a prison break, huh? That's cool, I guess.
You meet that Tina girl? Maya said she was... y'know... interesting.
If you ever run into Troy Calypso... you know what to do.
Maya's gone. Still doesn't feel real, ya know? I feel sick...
You freed Hammerlock, huh? That's cool, that's cool. Wish I could get off this ship sometime and, ya know, do somethin'... just sayin'.
Anyone who allies with Troy Calypso deserves a knife in the throat. If you don't take Aurelia out, I will.
Troy's using Maya's powers for THAT?! UGH! Bastard!
First Maliwan and Atlas go to war. Now the COV take over Jakobs. It has not been a good year for corporations... well, unless you're a gun manufacturer... so... ugh, nevermind.
Why are we goin' after the stupid Vault?! Let's find the Calypsos, chain them to Marcus's shooting range, and go to town! Right?!
Can I get in on this Jakobs resistance thing? I am seriously going insane on this ship. If Claptrap tells me one more time about his “epic birthday party”, he's gonna have an accident by the airlock.
So, Aurelia's dead, huh? Guess that frees up your schedule for Troy, right?
Glad that Aurelia bitch got taken out. Serves her right.
The Calypsos kidnapped Tannis... you're gonna find her, right?
So... back to Pandora, huh? Maya told me stories of Vault Hunting there. Sounds dangerous. And exciting. And dangerous.
Tannis. Tannis is a Siren. You've gotta be kidding me.
When do I get to be a Siren? Seriously!
That Carnivora thing was friggin' WILD. If you're keeping tabs, that's what I want for my birthday. Then I'm gonna drive it real slow-like over Troy Calypso's junk.
Can you imagine how douchey Troy and Tyreen would be if they actually opened the Great Vault? We gotta stop 'em.
Man, that Vaughn guy is kinda up for anything, huh? Wonder what he did before becoming a bandit. Must've been something crazy.
I'm a Siren! Thanks to you. I'll make Maya proud...
I have absolutely no idea how to use my powers, but it's okay. I've got Claptrap as a test dummy.
Don't worry. We're gonna save Pandora and stop this. I know it.
Pandora's pretty doomed. I thought Athenas had it bad, but Pandora always seems to have it worse.
Typhon DeLeon is alive? That's crazy. He disappeared decades ago! Dude must have a story to tell! Seriously.
So... the Calypsos were Typhon DeLeon's kids?
I miss Maya. Just thinkin' about havin' to live up to her... I know I gotta try.
Imagine kids that turn out as monsters like Troy and Tyreen. Man, you'd spent the rest of your life tryin' to set things right. Whatever “right” is, ya know?
So... the Eridians built a machine to stop Pandora from opening. Makes sense. We've all got stuff that we wish we could take back, ya know?
I'm no fan of the Calypsos, but think about being stuck on Nekrotafeyo for your whole life. Maya used to say that not every prison has bars.
Typhon's gone... wherever he is, I hope he forgives himself.
You have to stop Tyreen, Vault Hunter. You're the only one who can, and you freakin' know it.
Pandora's still coming apart. Everything I know about the planet is that it's the absolute worst, but still, someone's gotta save it.
Tyreen. It all ends with Tyreen. You know what you have to do, Vault Hunter.
Concentrate. Maliwan troops could be just around the corner.
Maliwan will think twice before messing with Athenas again.
Tannis is gone... you have to find her, Vault Hunter.
Great. Now Tannis is a Siren?!||—Heh, heh. Kidding. Not kidding...
No more messing around. Let's take the fight to the Calypsos.
He's dead... finally. But we've got bigger problems, huh?
So? What's Typhon DeLeon like? Is he as heroic as in the stories?
The Machine... it's our last chance to set things right.
You have to stop Tyreen. No one else can. Seriously.
Wow... it's over. You did it! How good does THAT feel?
So... yeah.
Kinda thought being a Vault Hunter would involve a lot more... doing stuff. But this is cool too, I guess.
One time Maya grounded me for two weeks after I stole a monk's glass eye. I think I still have it somewhere...
Gotta find some new tunes. You'd think there's only two bands in the whole universe.
Nice job taking the fight to Maliwan, Vault Hunter.
Wow, you really saved Rhys' ass, huh?
Maya...
I just... I feel like... I don't know, never mind.
If you see Troy Calypso again, you know what to do.
Heard you're kickin' ass down there on Eden-6.
One fragment down, two to go. Nice!
You have to get to that Vault before the Calypsos. Promise me.
Got somethin' for ya when you're free.
If you're not busy, I could use some help.
Hey—drop by when you're free, yeah?
Oh, hey.
S'up, Vault Hunter.
Hey there!
Yo.
What up.
Hey, got somethin' for ya.
So, since you're already doin' stuff...
Yo, got a thing. Wanna do the thing?
I've got chores and you've got time. Think we can work somethin' out?
I've got a job I could totally do but I don't wanna. You wanna, right?
So... you gonna finish the thing?
Procrastinating? I get it.
Hey, go do that thing we talked about. Whenever. Not goin' anywhere.
How's that thing goin'?
You finished yet?
Later.
See ya.
Bye.
Laters.
Catch ya around.
See ya around.
So long.
Later, Vault Hunter.
What was I doing?
Hermes! Here, boy!
